{"tid":1059460,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"依家啲人搞個grad din 都要人感恩","createTime":"2019-03-13T06:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T13:11:40.000Z","uid":221256,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3a34e7582c05c03b403aee6fd389f7fd411e6abf","tid":1059460,"uid":221256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a5hhD90.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa5hhD90.png&h=77e06300&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實grad din係多謝老師<br />\n見朋友你自己約出黎啦...<br />\n事實上唔係真係個個學生都比得起,人地比唔起你就話人地窮係邊緣人?<br />\n咩叫幾百蚊嘈到咁.食餐飯幾百蚊好平?唔好意思,唔係個個好似佢咁出黎做.3萬蚊一晚有daddy幫佢比曬<br />\n考慮下人感受啦垃圾<br />\n<br />\n利申: 識佢本人 正牌model 雞 港女兼囗臭 <br />\n         我地學校出名多窮撚 佢就整個開價$800嘅grad din<br />\n         跟住屌9啲同學唔揀佢個$800 plan 頂級"},{"pid":"0a4fa7e73d655d302ff7c995b13de3c538726988","tid":1059460,"uid":193066,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T08:14:31.000Z","msg":"第一，一個普通中學生會無啦啦有能力畀八舊水Grad Din?<br />\n第二，肯定全世界都有朋友架啦，個個都會想去Grad din嘅。<br />\n第三，「謝師宴」係咪真係「謝師」呢？有心謝師，其實唔一定要透過grad din去做。"},{"pid":"f6ec82550e8957379dbaa5c7f057c3449323517e","tid":1059460,"uid":82398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T08:22:07.000Z","msg":"好多人成個中學生涯都俾幾個老師針對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地又唔講？"},{"pid":"509e49d51351a6d1eb4d368389a5f0d72e1ad431","tid":1059460,"uid":116407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:46:15.000Z","msg":"好簡單，去咪畀錢唔去咪唔畀，佢口中所講嘅協商咪又係幾個搞手圍威喂定個價錢出黎，你估大家都想謝師咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d14db189c0d72319ae3813af514a32064f458bd","tid":1059460,"uid":13013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:47:30.000Z","msg":"唔俾佢又奈我咩何呢"},{"pid":"eb5b4682442c370c5a60c633b0e434f09bda0d75","tid":1059460,"uid":155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:49:20.000Z","msg":"日日見就好撚熟咩<img